{"tid":1631862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨鐵話一再拆站好撚嬲喎～","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:26:57.000Z","uid":23707,"like":163,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":140,"replies":[{"pid":"e473cafa72f322de122c3a7c9720d6b2882a7fb2","tid":1631862,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h777wKY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh777wKY.png&h=8e76ac6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0abb19e3dbde32cd63972c1084a8fb02fb39de77","tid":1631862,"uid":135798,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"so?"},{"pid":"4819a52769222a625e98a64b91c57c6433ed7755","tid":1631862,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"82ed0105e2737d709ea6ea591e6464f4f048b340","tid":1631862,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1419d4a82599a314cd464420b9f87f7ac50f4e37","tid":1631862,"uid":252973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"67de28235ac945cdb79d77906c23287683827ff0","tid":1631862,"uid":125542,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"唔好開囖<br />\n賺香港人錢 出賣香港人"},{"pid":"bdb84dda698f6e62cd52446173c5d52b88169c25","tid":1631862,"uid":150083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"證明我們做對了"},{"pid":"34f0b9448627540732d914f53cf24c6901710d0a","tid":1631862,"uid":70264,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"一開始唔放差佬入地鐵<br />\n唔停站 就乜事都無<br />\n<br />\n不過扮乜同警察商討<br />\n根本港鐵就係政府一部份<br />\n人地落咩order都照跟啦"},{"pid":"d74426caa720491abd04df692f78f69176ed47f0","tid":1631862,"uid":53003,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"沙中綫、年年加價、又撞車又出軌問題，市民都好憤慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04320354fb9d41233a2b6c4197d44892872c5e0","tid":1631862,"uid":308423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:41.000Z","msg":"閱。"},{"pid":"ac011a00895a3ba6948b3934e8591a4c226c3633","tid":1631862,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"19babc844174e548baa9740a2b4909df17561cd1","tid":1631862,"uid":288351,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得淨係拆佢度門唔夠喉。想睇下攻入去站入面玩下係點"},{"pid":"acef493f0a27c3d3dbd662292321892d9f7016a7","tid":1631862,"uid":35860,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"19babc844174e548baa9740a2b4909df17561cd1","tid":1631862,"uid":288351,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得淨係拆佢度門唔夠喉。想睇下攻入去站入面玩下係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"入去參觀完幫佢封到實一實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜人都入唔番"},{"pid":"d0e3d962a1349d908d28706bcd66d4343aefa038","tid":1631862,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffd0b36acde6b81d1a0af7027d2299f8c6761bd","tid":1631862,"uid":33004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"年年加價又壞車我都好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪費我時間"},{"pid":"2931da7596519998b40ca909347d0dbcc6e7a02c","tid":1631862,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"好驚呀"},{"pid":"d94596224422ad55ebeef50e27882247b212b933","tid":1631862,"uid":76398,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"手足唔搞你，你自己都出軌自炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6dac69497d7932dc5a4f17a6b28f61ed49c091","tid":1631862,"uid":55130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"Where is 鐵路應變部隊?"},{"pid":"643c4564d302bbe26c5f120c39a5f07cdc0dbd76","tid":1631862,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"