rong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5e8c2146af4c00a5132c96bc023e428982a55121","tid":1631862,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com/g00/3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_/c-7NPSFQIFVT0x24iuuqtx3ax2fx2fjnh-t-nto-dpn.blbnbjafe.ofux2fufoboux2fbnqx2ffoujuzjex2fBBJmm0b.jnhx3fix3d711x26x78x3d861x26nx3d7x26rx3d71x26px3dgx26mx3dgx26j21d.nbslx3djnbhf_$/$/$/$/$\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc-7npsfqifvt0x24jnh-t-nto-dpnx2eblbnbjafex2eofu.g01.msn.com%2Fg00%2F3_c-7x78x78x78.nto.dpn_%2Fc-7NPSFQIFVT0x24iuuqtx3ax2fx2fjnh-t-nto-dpn.blbnbjafe.ofux2fufoboux2fbnqx2ffoujuzjex2fBBJmm0b.jnhx3fix3d711x26x78x3d861x26nx3d7x26rx3d71x26px3dgx26mx3dgx26j21d.nbslx3djnbhf_%24%2F%24%2F%24%2F%24%2F%24&h=ebabab8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來撞一撞個灑水器就會噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一搞又濕晒"},{"pid":"82ad862801354fa83468474398c76cd8a01a2498","tid":1631862,"uid":119343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"即係方向正確"},{"pid":"fc13c26451072401c1e889094111e859c285077d","tid":1631862,"uid":156064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"嬲嬲豬洗唔洗叔叔氹返呀咁🥺🥺<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母中共走狗歐陽伯權你個垃撚圾仆街死啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"9496d2bcf6b33964962a75c3f904b3fa39763083","tid":1631862,"uid":322922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<br />\nNoted<br />\n繼續"},{"pid":"f0f9b63626531eecf5aa50472d4b5f596fbab82d","tid":1631862,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"「從今日起，提早返工返學，搭黨鐵，和你迫<br />\n只上不落」<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n我地成日話見到勇武手足被捕受傷好唔忍心，但和理非又從來無行動升級。罷工攪極都攪唔成，有咩好講？<br />\n<br />\n拿，我依家諗到個方法，俾所有唔敢罷工、好撚鍾意返工既人參與，就係：<br />\n提早返工、搭黨鐵、唔落車<br />\n<br />\n唔該所有人提早一個鐘出門口，全部去搭黨鐵，係，平時唔搭既都要搭！（我知好多手足未必接受到，一陣又話我係鬼，但聽我講埋先！唔同意再屌，好無？）<br />\n<br />\n上左車，就一直搭到總站，中途唔使落車，總之淨係搭車，乜都唔使做，唔使阻人上落。你買左飛，搭黨鐵，無犯法、無問題。唔使戴口罩、唔使著黑衣，同平時一樣正常返工返學就得。你係普通巿民，無人會攪你，黨鐵職員、黑警都無你符<br />\n只要人夠多，令到人上唔到車，自然可以擴散個效應，癱瘓交通，黨鐵受影響，又會迫人搭返地面交通，就有可能癱瘓全城交通。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多人唔夠膽罷工，驚到時得我一個罷工咪死？拿，呢個我都幫你諗埋啦，你係早左一個鐘頭出門口，如果多人響應，癱瘓成功，你就大條道理同公司講返唔到工。但萬一真係無人響應，行動失敗，交通正常，你咪準時返工囉，專登提早左一個鐘出門口俾你做buffer架仆街！嗰日當乜事都無發生過。但一日失敗唔代表永遠失敗，日日keep住做，我相信咁樣做成間接罷工既機會率，重大過你地一直等永遠唔會出現既真罷工<br />\n<br />\n和理非、返工撚，如果咁低成本既行動你咁都唔肯做，唔好同我講你有幾支持運動、有幾擔心勇武<br />\n<br />\n從今日起，提早返工返學  搭黨鐵  唔落車  只上不落<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗"},{"pid":"90371a56d40f030343657aab7cf704cf3a021295","tid":1631862,"uid":52912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzBHq63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzBHq63.jpg&h=e9c1c81b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"060c42ce0ddcbcf2c86869eff1692a4bf4d16b98","tid":1631862,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"由放低散紙買飛 到被裝修，自己諗吓做過乜？"},{"pid":"daa49b389d48046cbb162c92e504bc66bfb94ffc","tid":1631862,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"叫淋病嚟呵番d閘機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d8005fae8d86035f9f8fb3aad5cf65646420c2","tid":1631862,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新口號：和勇相連 絕不割蓆！</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><b