x%2Fi%2FUxxWu2C.jpg&h=d297e2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六台聯合發佈<br />\n大家同我推上熱門！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非們出動啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要用呢度嘅平台去搵食<br />\n香港唔係淨係得渣哥同加藤屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有成千間黃店等緊大家去幫襯<br />\n多人絕對唔係藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度擺低哂我地平台link<br />\n<br />\n香港良心Guide (網頁+IG):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.leungsumshops.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leungsumshops.com%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=ca825c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.leungsumshops.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkshoplist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkshoplist%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=5b0383a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkshoplist/</a><br />\n<br />\n全民罷買日 Byebuyday (IG):<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=110rffoj3s8vs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%3Figshid%3D110rffoj3s8vs&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d281ef2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=110rffoj3s8vs</a><br />\n<br />\n黃業 (Telegram bot):<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ybshopbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fybshopbot&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=202fe6c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: