dwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望唔只爆買日，各位手足每一日都要幫襯黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e57b658fe879978ecec94d491d99af40a56e0a6b","tid":1631862,"uid":66346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"唔好俾黨鐵開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32be38106b9a7ef1df06260dac1efb3ed5d1e397","tid":1631862,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"so 24 hours 黑警駐守?"},{"pid":"dc16cc4ab3e90bbd786b5379dda3f0b38cf5da76","tid":1631862,"uid":144848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"我都好撚嬲<br />\n拆咁耐都仲唔撚爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要逼我返學？我想參加三罷行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8098acaa8f80f1c6baeaef00fad526ecdc4fa5","tid":1631862,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"如果要輕鐵停駛，每個輕鐵站必定一組淺藍色箱，係輕鐵站附近，好容易認嘅，通常會有一部冷氣放係頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29304ee2cea2222f01ff4d70eba62d40e930b031","tid":1631862,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"真心，等狗鐵整番好先"},{"pid":"d30d40f5138a25a95765e9da61b336caf5625e66","tid":1631862,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"我地都好憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1e996e13f7261d266921d055f05eaa088e1fe2","tid":1631862,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"敵人反應的我們就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3f3a67276b57c2a5de119d999afbe6ee6188dd","tid":1